# Hydna Lua Client Library

This first version of our client library for Lua implements support for the
Hydna Push API. Future versions will include support for the full set of
features.

More info: https://www.hydna.com/

## Dependencies

- LuaSocket

## Usage

The `hydna`-module exposes two functions:

    local hydna = require hydna

    # send a message
    hydna.send('public.hydna.net', 'hello world from lua')

    # emit a signal
    hydna.emit('public.hydna.net', 'hello world from lua')


## Limitations

This version does not include support for binary data.